      "span_text": "Similar to our results, maximal decolorization of RBBR and BPB (around 80%) occurred after 30 min at 30˝C using 6.5 U¨mL´1 of a purified laccase from T. trogii BAFC 463 while a three-fold higher enzyme load was required to obtain a similar level of decolorization using the crude culture extract [CITATION_1] ."
